# TypeScript

## Formatting (ESLint)

- No trailing comma: `commaDangle: 'never'`
- Brace style: `1tbs` (opening brace on same line)

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
const obj = {
  foo: 1,
}

// ✅ GOOD
const obj = {
  foo: 1
}
```

## Nuxt auto-imports

Use Nuxt auto-imports: `defineEventHandler`, `useRoute`, `useAsyncData`, `computed`, `provide`, `inject` – no manual imports needed.

## Server API

- Handlers in `server/api/` – `defineEventHandler`
- MCP tools in `server/mcp/tools/`
- Routes in `server/routes/`
